Original Mod: Deathbell Princess by [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/4958627]Loshirai14[/url]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28788

This is standalone, and it won't work if you have the original mod because they use the same .esp.

This mod is for vanilla or SAM bodies. SAM means shape atlas for men. 
Google it, it's great.
